"When the displayed information is correct, click :guilabel:`Next Step` and "
"the status changes to :guilabel:`Bank Details`. Using the drop-down menu, "
"select the :guilabel:`Bank Journal` for payroll. After a journal is "
"selected, the :guilabel:`Bank Name`, :guilabel:`Account "
