msgstr ""
"Flera sektioner i konfigurationsmenyn (Inställningar, Lönestrukturer & "
"regler, Arbetsposttyper, Arbetsschema, |MPF| Schema) definierar specifika "
"lokaliseringsregler för Hongkong."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:90
msgid "Advantages"
msgstr "Förmåner"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:92
msgid ""
":guilabel:`HK: Internet Subscription`: Add a default monthly internet "
"allowance."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`HK: Internetabonnemang`: Lägg till ett standardmånadsbelopp för "
"internet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`End of Year Payments Month`: Select the month to automatically "
"add end-of-year payments to payslips (if any)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Månad för utbetalningar vid årets slut`: Välj månad för att "
"automatiskt lägga till utbetalningar vid årets slut till lönespecifikationer "
"(om några)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use MPF Offsetting`: Enable this to define pre-set and post-set "
"offset periods for calculating Severance Payments (SP) and Long Service "
"Payments (LSP)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Använd MPF-kompensation`: Aktivera detta för att definiera "
"fördefinierade och efterdefinierade kompensationsperioder för beräkning av "
"avgångsvederlag (SP) och långtjänstbetalningar (LSP)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "The Hong Kong Localization section in Payroll Settings."
msgstr "Avsnittet för Hongkong-lokalisering i Löneinställningar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:102
msgid ""
"The Advantages section is optional. Configuring benefits here applies the "
"same value to all employees, reducing manual configuration."
msgstr ""
"Avsnittet Förmåner är valfritt. Att konfigurera förmåner här tillämpar samma "
"värde på alla anställda, vilket minskar manuell konfiguration."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:106
msgid "Accounting section"
msgstr "Bokföringsavsnitt"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:108
msgid "Configure the entries for the :guilabel:`Accounting` section:"
msgstr "Konfigurera posterna för avsnittet :guilabel:`Bokföring`:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:110
msgid ":guilabel:`Payroll HSBC Autopay`: Enable to create HSBC payment files."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Payroll HSBC Autopay`: Aktivera för att skapa HSBC-"
"betalningsfiler."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:111
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Batch Account Move Lines`: Enable to merge all accounting entries "
"for the same period into a single account move line. This anonymizes "
"accounting entries but disables single payment generations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Batch-verifikationsrader`: Aktivera för att sammanfoga alla "
"bokföringsposter för samma period till en enda verifikationsrad. Detta "
"anonymiserar bokföringsposter men inaktiverar generering av enskilda "
"betalningar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "The Accounting section in Payroll Settings."
msgstr "Bokföringsavsnittet i Löneinställningar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:121
msgid "Structures & rules"
msgstr "Strukturer och regler"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:123
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Structures --> "
"Rules` to check salary rules or configure specific company salary rules."
msgstr ""
"Navigera till :menuselection:`Löner-app --> Konfiguration --> Strukturer --> "
"Regler` för att kontrollera löneregler eller konfigurera specifika "
"företagslöneregler."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:127
msgid "CAP57: Employees Monthly Pay"
msgstr "CAP57: Anställdas månadslöner"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:129
msgid ""
"Odoo provides the :guilabel:`CAP57: Employees Monthly Pay` salary structure "
"to calculate compliant payroll for regular employees. The following salary "
"rules are mandatory, which are added automatically to payslips:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo tillhandahåller lönestrukturen :guilabel:`CAP57: Anställdas "
"månadslöner` för att beräkna kompatibel lön för reguljära anställda. "
"Följande löneregler är obligatoriska och läggs automatiskt till i "
"lönespecifikationer:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:133
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rent Allowance`: Amount derived from the employee's active rental "
"record."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hyresersättning`: Belopp härlett från den anställdes aktiva "
"uthyrningspost."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Basic Salary`: Amount of base salary provided (after rent "
"allowance deduction)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Grundlön`: Belopp för grundlön som tillhandahålls (efter avdrag "
"för hyresersättning)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:135
msgid ""
":guilabel:`713 Gross`: Net payable amount considering commissions, internet "
"allowance, reimbursements, back-pay, deductions, etc."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`713 Brutto`: Nettoutbetalningsbelopp med hänsyn till provisioner, "
"internetersättning, återbetalningar, efterbetalning, avdrag osv."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`MPF Gross`: Net payable amount from 713 gross after consideration "
"of additional allowances, deductions, and end-of-year payment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`MPF-brutto`: Nettoutbetalningsbelopp från 713 brutto efter hänsyn "
"till ytterligare ersättningar, avdrag och utbetalning vid årets slut."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:139
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employee Mandatory Contribution`: Mandatory employee |MPF| "
"contribution."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Employee Mandatory Contribution`: anställdas MPF-bidrag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employer Mandatory Contribution`: Mandatory employer |MPF| "
"contribution."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Employer Mandatory Contribution`: arbetsgivarens MPF-bidrag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:141
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employee Voluntary Contribution`: Voluntary employee contribution "
"(if any)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Anställds frivilliga bidrag`: Frivilligt bidrag från anställd (om "
"något)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:142
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employer Voluntary Contribution`: Voluntary employer contribution "
"(if any)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbetsgivarens frivilliga bidrag`: Frivilligt arbetsgivarbidrag "
"(om något)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:143
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employer Voluntary Contribution 2`: Additional voluntary employer "
"contribution (if any)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbetsgivarens frivilliga bidrag 2`: Ytterligare frivilligt "
"arbetsgivarbidrag (om något)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:145
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Gross`: Net payable amount from |MPF| gross after consideration "
"of |MPF| deductions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gross`: nettobelopp som ska betalas från MPF brutto efter "
"beaktande av MPF avdrag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:146
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Net Salary`: Final payable amount to be paid to the employee."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nettolön`: Slutligt utbetalningsbelopp som ska betalas till den "
"anställde."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:148
msgid ""
"The following salary rules are optional rules for employee benefits, which "
"can be manually added as salary inputs in the payslip under "
"the :guilabel:`Salary Inputs` tab:"
msgstr ""
"Följande löneregler är valfria regler för personalförmåner, som kan läggas "
"till manuellt som löneindata i lönebeskedet under "
"fliken :guilabel:`Löneindata`:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:151
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Back Pay`: Additional salary payout can be included under this "
"category."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Efterbetalning`: Ytterligare löneutbetalning kan inkluderas under "
"denna kategori."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:152
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Commission`: The commission earned during the period can be "
"manually entered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Provision`: Provisionen som intjänats under perioden kan anges "
"manuellt."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Global Deduction`: A lump-sum deduction from the entire payslip."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Globalt avdrag`: Ett engångsavdrag från hela lönebeskedet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:154
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Global Reimbursement`: A lump-sum reimbursement to the entire "
"payslip."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Global ersättning`: En engångsersättning till hela lönebeskedet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:155
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Referral Fee`: The additional bonus offered for any form of "
"business-related referral."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Remissavgift`: Den ytterligare bonus som erbjuds för någon form "
"av affärsrelaterad remiss."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:156
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Moving Daily Wage`: To override the ADW value used for leave "
"computation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rörlig dagslön`: För att åsidosätta ADW-värdet som används för "
"ledighetsberäkning."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:157
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Skip Rent Allowance`: If set, the rental allowance is excluded "
"from the current payslip."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hoppa över hyresersättning`: Om satt exkluderas hyresersättningen "
"från det aktuella lönebeskedet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:159
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Custom Average Monthly Salary`: To override the average monthly "
"salary used for end-of-year payment (rule is only applicable to payslips "
"generated in December)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Anpassad genomsnittlig månadslön`: För att åsidosätta den "
"genomsnittliga månadslönen som används för årsslutbetalning (regeln är "
"endast tillämplig på lönebesked genererade i december)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:163
msgid "CAP57: Payment in Lieu of Notice"
msgstr "CAP57: Betalning i stället för uppsägning"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:165
msgid ""
"Odoo provides the :guilabel:`CAP57: Payment in Lieu of Notice` salary "
"structure to process a final payment to an employee in place of serving a "
"required notice period upon termination."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tillhandahåller lönestrukturen :guilabel:`CAP57: Betalning i stället "
"för uppsägning` för att behandla en slutbetalning till en anställd i stället "
"för att tjänstgöra en obligatorisk uppsägningstid vid uppsägning."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:168
msgid ""
"Mandatory rule for this salary structure which is automatically added to the "
"payslip:"
msgstr ""
"Obligatorisk regel för denna lönestruktur som automatiskt läggs till i "
"lönebeskedet:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:170
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment in Lieu of Notice`: This is the calculated amount paid to "
"the employee corresponding to the unserved notice period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Betalning i stället för uppsägning`: Detta är det beräknade "
"beloppet som betalas till den anställde motsvarande den ej tjänstgjorda "
"uppsägningstiden."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:173
msgid ""
"Optional rule for this salary structure which can be manually added as a "
"salary input in the payslip under the :guilabel:`Salary Inputs` tab:"
msgstr ""
"Valfri regel för denna lönestruktur som kan läggas till manuellt som "
"löneindata i lönebeskedet under fliken :guilabel:`Löneindata`:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:176
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Lieu of Notice Period (Months)`: Only applicable to the `CAP57: "
"Payment in Lieu of Notice` salary structure. By default, the final payout is "
"set to 1-month. Use the :guilabel:`Count` field under the salary inputs tab "
"to set a different notice period duration."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uppsägningstid i stället för uppsägning (månader)`: Endast "
"tillämplig på lönestrukturen `CAP57: Betalning i stället för uppsägning`. "
"Som standard är den slutliga utbetalningen inställd på 1 månad. Använd "
"fältet :guilabel:`Antal` under fliken löneindata för att ange en annan "
"giltighetstid för uppsägningstiden."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:181
msgid "CAP57: Long Service Payment (LSP)"
msgstr "CAP57: Långtjänstbetalning (LSP)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:183
msgid ""
"Odoo provides the :guilabel:`CAP57: Long Service Payment` salary structure "
"to process an employee whose continuous employment with the employer, under "
"a contract of employment, reaches 5 years."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tillhandahåller lönestrukturen :guilabel:`CAP57: Long Service Payment` "
"för att behandla en anställd vars sammanhängande anställning hos "
"arbetsgivaren, enligt ett anställningsavtal, når 5 år."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:186
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:213
msgid ""
"Mandatory rules for this salary structure which are automatically added to "
"the payslip:"
msgstr ""
"Obligatoriska regler för denna lönestruktur som automatiskt läggs till i "
"lönebeskedet:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:188
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Long Service Payment`: The final calculated amount of long "
"service payment paid to the employee (after applying offsets, if any)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Long Service Payment`: Det slutliga beräknade beloppet för long "
"service payment som betalas till den anställde (efter tillämpning av "
"avräkningar, om några)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:190
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Long Service Payment Pre Transition`: The portion of the long "
"service payment calculated based on the employment period before the "
"transition date of the offsetting arrangement, where |MPF| contributions can "
"still be used to offset the payment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Betalning för långtjänstgöring före övergång`: Den del av "
"betalningen för långtjänstgöring som beräknas baserat på "
"anställningsperioden före övergångsdatumet för kvittningsarrangemanget, där |"
"MPF|-avgifter fortfarande kan användas för att kvitta betalningen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:193
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Long Service Payment Post Transition`: The portion of the long "
"service payment calculated based on the employment period on or after the "
"transition date of the offsetting arrangement."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Long Service Payment Post Transition`: Den del av long service "
"payment som beräknas baserat på anställningsperioden på eller efter "
"övergångsdatumet för avräkningsarrangemanget."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:197
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:223
msgid ""
"Enable :guilabel:`Use MPF Offsetting` in the Hong Kong localization section "
"to use these offset salary rules:"
msgstr ""
"Aktivera :guilabel:`Use MPF Offsetting` i Hongkong-lokaliseringssektionen "
"för att använda dessa avräkningsregler för lön:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:200
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:226
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pre-transition Offset`: The amount of |MPF| contribution (or "
"benefits from an :abbr:`ORSO (Occupational Retirement Schemes Ordinance)` "
"scheme) that can be used to offset the pre-transition amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kvittning före övergång`: Beloppet av |MPF|-avgift (eller "
"förmåner från ett :abbr:`ORSO (Occupational Retirement Schemes Ordinance)`-"
"system) som kan användas för att kvitta beloppet före övergången."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:203
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:229
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Post-transition Offset`: The amount of |MPF| contribution (or "
"benefits from an :abbr:`ORSO (Occupational Retirement Schemes Ordinance)` "
"scheme) that can be used to offset the post-transition amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kvittning efter övergång`: Beloppet av |MPF|-avgift (eller "
"förmåner från ett :abbr:`ORSO (Occupational Retirement Schemes Ordinance)`-"
"system) som kan användas för att kvitta beloppet efter övergången."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:208
msgid "CAP57: Severance Payment (SP)"
msgstr "CAP57: Avgångsvederlag (SP)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:210
msgid ""
"Odoo provides the :guilabel:`CAP57: Severance Payment` salary structure to "
"process an employee whose continuous employment with the employer, under a "
"contract of employment, reaches 2 years."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tillhandahåller lönestrukturen :guilabel:`CAP57: Severance Payment` för "
"att behandla en anställd vars sammanhängande anställning hos arbetsgivaren, "
"enligt ett anställningsavtal, når 2 år."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:215
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Severance Payment`: The final calculated amount of severance "
"payment paid to the employee (after applying offsets, if any)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Severance Payment`: Det slutliga beräknade beloppet för "
"avgångsvederlag som betalas till den anställde (efter tillämpning av "
"avräkningar, om några)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:217
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Severance Payment Pre Transition`: The portion of the severance "
"payment calculated based on the employment period before the transition date "
"of the offsetting arrangement, where |MPF| contributions can still be used "
"to offset the payment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Avgångsvederlag före övergång`: Den del av avgångsvederlaget som "
"beräknas baserat på anställningsperioden före övergångsdatumet för "
"kvittningsarrangemanget, där |MPF|-avgifter fortfarande kan användas för att "
"kvitta betalningen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:220
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Severance Payment Post Transition`: The portion of the severance "
"payment calculated based on the employment period on or after the transition "
"date of the offsetting arrangement."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Severance Payment Post Transition`: Den del av avgångsvederlaget "
"som beräknas baserat på anställningsperioden på eller efter övergångsdatumet "
"för avräkningsarrangemanget."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:238
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Work Entries --"
"> Work Entry Types` to check work entry types or configure a new work entry "
"type."
msgstr ""
"Navigera till :menuselection:`Löner-app --> Konfiguration --> Arbetsposter --"
"> Arbetsposttyper` för att kontrollera arbetsposttyper eller konfigurera en "
"ny arbetsposttyp."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:241
msgid "In defining each work entry type for Hong Kong, employers can define:"
msgstr ""
"När arbetsgivare definierar varje arbetsposttyp för Hongkong kan de ange:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:243
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rate`: The rate that is used to calculate for each leave (e.g., "
"80% for sick leave)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Anrop`: Den sats som används för att beräkna varje ledighet "
"(t.ex. 80% för sjukledighet)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:244
msgid ""
":guilabel:`ADW Calculation`: Enable this to calculate the employee's pay "
"according to the Average Daily Wage (ADW) rules under Hong Kong employment "
"regulations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ADW Calculation`: Aktivera detta för att beräkna den anställdes "
"lön enligt reglerna för Average Daily Wage (ADW) enligt Hongkongs "
"anställningsbestämmelser."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "Configuration screen for an 80 percent Sick Leave Work Entry Type."
msgstr "Konfigurationsskärm för en 80-procentig sjukledighetsarbetsposttyp."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:250
msgid ""
"Odoo supports 11 HK-specific work entry types which are used together with "
"the **Time Off** app:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo stöder 11 HK-specifika arbetsposttyper som används tillsammans med "
"**Ledighet**-appen:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:252
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sick Leave 80%`: Paid sick leave compensated at 80% of the "
"employee's average daily wage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sick Leave 80%`: Betald sjukledighet kompenserad med 80% av den "
"anställdes genomsnittliga daglön."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:254
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Compassionate Leave`: Leave granted for personal emergencies, "
"such as the death of a family member."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ledighet vid dödsfall`: Ledighet som beviljas vid personliga "
"nödsituationer, såsom dödsfall i familjen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:256
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Marriage Leave`: Time off granted to an employee for their "
"wedding."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bröllopsledighet`: Ledighet som beviljas en anställd för sitt "
"bröllop."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:257
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Examination Leave`: Leave granted to an employee to take "
"professional examinations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tentamensledighet`: Ledighet som beviljas en anställd för att "
"avlägga yrkesprov."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:258
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Maternity Leave`: Statutory leave granted to female employees for "
"childbirth."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Föräldraledighet`: Lagstadgad ledighet som beviljas kvinnliga "
"anställda för barnafödande."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:259
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Maternity Leave 80%`: Maternity leave compensated at 80% of the "
"average daily wage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Föräldraledighet 80%`: Föräldraledighet som kompenseras med 80% "
"av genomsnittlig dagslön."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:260
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Paternity Leave`: Statutory leave granted to male employees "
"following a child's birth."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Faderskapssledighet`: Lagstadgad ledighet som beviljas manliga "
"anställda efter ett barns födelse."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:261
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Statutory Holiday`: Mandatory public holidays recognized by Hong "
"Kong employment law."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lagstadgad helgdag`: Obligatoriska allmänna helgdagar som erkänns "
"av Hongkongs arbetsrättslagstiftning."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:262
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Public Holiday`: General holidays observed by banks and "
"businesses in Hong Kong."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Offentlig helgdag`: Allmänna helgdagar som iakttas av banker och "
"företag i Hongkong."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:263
msgid ":guilabel:`Weekend`: Standard non-working days for the employee."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Helg`: Vanliga icke-arbetsdagar för den anställda."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:268
msgid "MPF schemes"
msgstr "MPF-system"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:270
msgid ""
"Odoo allows multiple |MPF| scheme configurations (currently 24 schemes), "
"creation of new schemes, different |MPF| groups and member classes, and "
"definition of income for automated |MPF| calculations. In alignment with "
"eMPF requirements, Odoo-generated eMPF contribution reports are ready to "
"upload to the `eMPF portal <https://www.empf.org.hk/?language_id=1>`_."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tillåter flera |MPF|-systemkonfigurationer (för närvarande 24 system), "
"skapande av nya system, olika |MPF|-grupper och medlemsklasser, samt "
"definition av inkomst för automatiserade |MPF|-beräkningar. I linje med eMPF-"
"krav är Odoo-genererade eMPF-avgiftsrapporter redo att laddas upp till `eMPF-"
"portalen <https://www.empf.org.hk/?language_id=1>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:276
msgid "Configuring an eMPF scheme"
msgstr "Konfigurera ett eMPF-system"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:278
msgid "Follow these steps to configure an eMPF scheme:"
msgstr "Följ dessa steg för att konfigurera ett eMPF-system:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:280
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` or select an eMPF scheme to configure. Enter "
"the :guilabel:`Employer Account No.` (this value is specific to the current "
"company)."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa` eller välj ett eMPF-system att konfigurera. "
"Ange :guilabel:`Arbetsgivarkontonummer` (detta värde är specifikt för det "
"aktuella företaget)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:282
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to create new payroll groups (used for "
"mandatory contributions) and member classes (used for voluntary "
"contributions)."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på :guilabel:`Lägg till en rad` för att skapa nya lönegrupper "
"(används för obligatoriska avgifter) och medlemsklasser (används för "
"frivilliga avgifter)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:286
msgid ""
"Employers can define one default payroll group or member class which is "
"shown as the default selection upon |MPF| selection whenever creating new "
"employees in :menuselection:`Employees --> Payroll --> MPF`."
msgstr ""
"Arbetsgivare kan definiera en standard lönegrupp eller medlemsklass som "
"visas som standardval vid |MPF|-val när nya anställda skapas "
"i :menuselection:`Anställda --> Löner --> MPF`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:290
msgid ""
"In creating a member class, click :guilabel:`View` to configure each "
"contribution type, option, amount of income, and definition of income."
msgstr ""
"När du skapar en medlemsklass klickar du på :guilabel:`Visa` för att "
"konfigurera varje avgiftstyp, alternativ, inkomstbelopp och definition av "
"inkomst."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:293
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contribution Type`: Select :guilabel:`Employee's Voluntary "
"Contribution`, :guilabel:`Employer's Voluntary Contribution`, "
"or :guilabel:`Employer's Voluntary Contribution 2`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Avgiftstyp`: Välj :guilabel:`Anställds frivilliga "
"avgift`, :guilabel:`Arbetsgivares frivilliga avgift` "
"eller :guilabel:`Arbetsgivares frivilliga avgift 2`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:295
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Option`: Defines how much voluntary contribution is calculated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Alternativ`: Definierar hur mycket frivillig avgift som beräknas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:297
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fixed Percentage of Income`: Contribution according to a "
"percentage."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Fast procentsats av inkomst`: Avgift enligt en procentsats."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:298
msgid ":guilabel:`Fixed Amount`: Contribution according to a fixed amount."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Fast belopp`: Bidrag enligt ett fast belopp."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:299
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Match Employee's Voluntary Contribution`: Contribution matches "
"the employee's voluntary contribution."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Matcha anställds frivilliga bidrag`: Bidrag matchar den anställds "
"frivilliga bidrag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:301
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fixed Percentage of Income minus Mandatory Contribution`: "
"Contribution capped with mandatory contribution."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fast procentsats av inkomst minus obligatoriskt bidrag`: Bidrag "
"begränsat med obligatoriskt bidrag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:304
msgid ":guilabel:`Amount`: Amount to apply as a percentage or fixed amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Belopp`: Belopp att tillämpa som procentsats eller fast belopp."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:305
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Definition of Income`: Define which income is used to calculate "
"voluntary contributions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Definition av inkomst`: Definiera vilken inkomst som används för "
"att beräkna frivilliga bidrag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:308
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Relevant Wages`: Based on all wages (commissions, bonuses, etc.) "
"the employee receives after calculation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Relevanta löner`: Baserat på alla löner (provisioner, bonusar "
"osv.) som den anställde erhåller efter beräkning."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:310
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Basic Wage`: Based on the basic wage (wage on contract) the "
"employee receives."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Grundlön`: Baserat på grundlönen (lön enligt avtal) som den "
"anställde erhåller."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid ""
"Configuration screen for |MPF| member classes and voluntary contributions."
msgstr "Konfigurationsskärm för |MPF|-medlemsklasser och frivilliga avgifter."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:318
msgid "Employee configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration av anställd"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:320
msgid ""
"To create an employee record, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Employees --> Employees`. Click :guilabel:`New` in the upper-left corner. "
"Fill in the primary contact details, then configure the following tabs:"
msgstr ""
"För att skapa en anställdpost, navigera till :menuselection:`Löner-appen --> "
"Anställda --> Anställda`. Klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa` i övre vänstra hörnet. "
"Fyll i primära kontaktuppgifter och konfigurera sedan följande flikar:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:327
msgid "Under the :guilabel:`Work` tab, configure organizational information."
msgstr "Under fliken :guilabel:`Arbete`, konfigurera organisationsinformation."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:329
msgid ":guilabel:`Work`: Set department, job title, and manager."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Arbete`: Ange avdelning, jobbtitel och chef."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:330
msgid ":guilabel:`Departure`: Only visible after archiving an employee record."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Avgång`: Endast synlig efter arkivering av en anställdpost."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:332
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Departure reason`: Used in eMPF reports for termination payment "
"checks."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Avgångsorsak`: Används i eMPF-rapporter för kontroll av "
"avgångsvederlag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:333
msgid ":guilabel:`Departure date`: Used in IR56 forms."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Avgångsdatum`: Används i IR56-formulär."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:338
msgid "Under the :guilabel:`Personal` tab, configure personal information."
msgstr ""
"Under fliken :guilabel:`Personligt`, konfigurera personlig information."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:340
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Private Contact`: Set surname, given name, name in Chinese (if "
"any), private email, phone number, and bank accounts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privat kontakt`: Ange efternamn, förnamn, namn på kinesiska (om "
"tillämpligt), privat e-post, telefonnummer och bankkonton."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:342
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Personal information`: Set employee legal name, birth date, and "
"gender."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Personlig information`: Ange anställds juridiska namn, "
"födelsedatum och kön."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:343
msgid ":guilabel:`Identification No`: Set the HKID of the employee."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Identifikationsnr`: Ange den anställdes HKID."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:344
msgid ":guilabel:`Location`: Set :guilabel:`Private Address`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Plats`: Ange :guilabel:`Privatadress`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:347
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Bank Account` needs to be marked as *trusted*. Having an "
"untrusted bank account for an employee causes an error in the pay run. To "
"achieve this, click on the right-arrow button next to the bank account "
"number field. Set the :guilabel:`Send Money to` field to :guilabel:`Trusted` "
"by clicking on the toggle."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bankkonto` måste markeras som *betrott*. Att ha ett icke-betrott "
"bankkonto för en anställd orsakar ett fel i löneutbetalningen. För att uppnå "
"detta, klicka på högerpilsknappen bredvid fältet för bankkontonummer. Ställ "
"in fältet :guilabel:`Skicka pengar till` till :guilabel:`Betrott` genom att "
"klicka på växlingsknappen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "Employee bank account configuration set to Trusted."
msgstr "Anställds bankkontokonfiguration inställd på Betrott."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:356
msgid "Mandatory personal information for government reports:"
msgstr "Obligatorisk personlig information för statliga rapporter:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:358
msgid ""
"|MPF|: :guilabel:`Surname`, :guilabel:`Given Name`, :guilabel:`Name in "
"Chinese`, :guilabel:`Phone`, :guilabel:`Birthday`, :guilabel:`Private "
"Address`, :guilabel:`Identification No` / :guilabel:`Passport No`."
msgstr ""
"|MPF|: :guilabel:`Efternamn`, :guilabel:`Förnamn`, :guilabel:`Namn på "
"kinesiska`, :guilabel:`Telefon`, :guilabel:`Födelsedag`, :guilabel:`Privat "
"adress`, :guilabel:`Identifikationsnummer` / :guilabel:`Passnummer`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:362
msgid ""
"|IRD| Reports: :guilabel:`Surname`, :guilabel:`Given "
"Name`, :guilabel:`Phone`, :guilabel:`Birthday`, :guilabel:`Gender`, :guilabel:`Identification "
"No` / :guilabel:`Passport No`."
msgstr ""
"|IRD|-"
"rapporter: :guilabel:`Efternamn`, :guilabel:`Förnamn`, :guilabel:`Telefon`, :guilabel:`Födelsedag`, :guilabel:`Kön`, :guilabel:`Identifikationsnummer` / :guilabel:`Passnummer`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:372
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract`: Select contract start and end dates for contract "
"management."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Avtal`: Välj avtals start- och slutdatum för avtalshantering."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:373
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage Type`: Select :guilabel:`Fixed Wage` or :guilabel:`Hourly "
"Wage`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lönetyp`: Välj :guilabel:`Fast lön` eller :guilabel:`Timlön`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:374
msgid ":guilabel:`Wage`: Define the employee's monthly wage."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Lön`: Definiera den anställdes månadslön."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:375
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pay Category`: Select :guilabel:`CAP57: Hong Kong Employee` for "
"monthly Hong Kong payroll calculations. This defines when the employee is "
"paid, their default working schedule, and the work entry type it applies to."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lönekategori`: Välj :guilabel:`CAP57: Hong Kong-anställd` för "
"månatliga löneberäkningar i Hong Kong. Detta definierar när den anställde "
"får betalt, deras standardarbetsschema och vilken arbetsposttyp det gäller "
"för."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:380
msgid ""
"When the hourly wage option is selected, the :guilabel:`Hourly Wage` field "
"is displayed to input the employee's hourly rate. You shouldn't put any "
"value in the :guilabel:`Wage` field for hourly paid employees, as that field "
"is based on monthly pay."
msgstr ""
"När alternativet timlön är valt visas fältet :guilabel:`Timlön` för att ange "
"den anställdes timtaxa. Du bör inte ange något värde i "
"fältet :guilabel:`Lön` för timavlönade anställda, eftersom det fältet "
"baseras på månadslön."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "The Contract Overview section under the Payroll tab."
msgstr "Sektionen Avtalsöversikt under fliken Löner."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:390
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Entry Source`: Select either :guilabel:`Working "
"Schedule`, :guilabel:`Attendances`, or :guilabel:`Planning`. This field "
"determines how the work entries are accounted for in the payslip."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbetspostkälla`: Välj "
"antingen :guilabel:`Arbetsschema`, :guilabel:`Närvaro` "
"eller :guilabel:`Planering`. Detta fält bestämmer hur arbetsposterna "
"redovisas i lönebeskedet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:394
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Schedule`: Work entries are generated automatically based "
"on the employee's working schedule."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbetsschema`: Arbetsposten genereras automatiskt baserat på den "
"anställdes arbetsschema."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:396
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Attendances`: Work entries are generated based on the check-in "
"and check-out period logged in the **Attendances** app."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Närvaro`: Arbetsposten genereras baserat på den in- och "
"utcheckningsperiod som loggats i appen **Närvaro**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:398
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Planning`: Work entries are generated from planning shifts only."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Planering`: Arbetsposten genereras endast från planerade "
"arbetspass."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:400
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Hours`: Select :guilabel:`HK Standard 40 hours/week` or "
"any newly created working schedule."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbetstid`: Välj :guilabel:`HK Standard 40 timmar/vecka` eller "
"något nyskapat arbetsschema."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:404
msgid "MPF section"
msgstr "MPF-sektion"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:406
msgid ":guilabel:`Exempt of MPF`: Enable this option for MPF-exempt employees."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Befriad från MPF`: Aktivera detta alternativ för MPF-befriade "
"anställda."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:407
msgid ":guilabel:`MPF Scheme`: Select the |MPF| scheme."
msgstr ":guilabel:`MPF-system`: Välj |MPF|-systemet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:408
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Member Account No.`: Enter the employee's member account number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Medlemskontonummer`: Ange den anställdes medlemskontonummer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:409
msgid ":guilabel:`Payroll Group`: Select the |MPF| payroll group."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Lönegrupp`: Välj |MPF|-lönegruppen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:410
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Member Class`: Select the |MPF| member class for voluntary "
"contributions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Medlemsklass`: Välj |MPF|-medlemsklassen för frivilliga avgifter."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:411
msgid ":guilabel:`Registration Status`: Define employee status."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Registreringsstatus`: Definiera anställds status."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:413
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Registration At Next Contribution`: Select for enrolling a new |"
"MPF| member."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Registrering vid nästa avgift`: Välj för att registrera en ny |"
"MPF|-medlem."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:414
msgid ":guilabel:`Registered`: Select for an existing |MPF| member."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Registrerad`: Välj för en befintlig |MPF|-medlem."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:415
msgid ":guilabel:`Terminated`: Select for a terminated |MPF| member."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Avslutad`: Välj för en avslutad |MPF|-medlem."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:417
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Start Contribution`: Define the contribution starting period for "
"new or existing members."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Börja avgift`: Definiera avgiftens startperiod för nya eller "
"befintliga medlemmar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:420
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Immediately Upon Registration`: Start contribution after "
"registering |MPF|, starting from the first payslip."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Omedelbart vid registrering`: Börja avgift efter registrering av |"
"MPF|, från och med första lönespecifikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:422
msgid ""
":guilabel:`At Due Date`: Start contribution after the contribution holiday "
"period. This starts its contribution mostly in the second or third payslip."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vid förfallodatum`: Börja avgift efter avgiftsfrihetsperioden. "
"Detta startar avgiften oftast i det andra eller tredje lönebeskedet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:425
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Date of Joining the Scheme`: Leave empty to set the date "
"automatically upon registration through the eMPF contribution report date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum för anslutning till systemet`: Lämna tomt för att ställa in "
"datumet automatiskt vid registrering genom eMPF-avgiftsrapportdatum."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "The MPF configuration section on the employee form."
msgstr "MPF-konfigurationssektionen på anställdformuläret."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:432
msgid "Benefits section"
msgstr "Förmånssektion"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:434
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Internet Subscription`: Set an additional internet allowance on "
"top of the current salary package."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Internetabonnemang`: Ställ in ett extra internetbidrag utöver det "
"nuvarande lönepaketet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:436
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Current Rental`: Configure rental information that is used as a "
"rental allowance in the payslip for the IR56B reporting period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aktuell uthyrning`: Konfigurera hyresinformation som används som "
"hyresbidrag i lönebeskedet för IR56B-rapporteringsperioden."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:439
msgid ""
"To create a rental record, click the :guilabel:`History` button near the "
"current rental field. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a rental history. "
"Enter the rental reference, rental start date, rental end date, rental type, "
"rental amount, and address. Change the rental status to :guilabel:`Running`."
msgstr ""
"För att skapa en uthyrningspost, klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Historik` nära "
"det aktuella uthyrningsfältet. Klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa` för att skapa en "
"uthyrningshistorik. Ange uthyrningsreferens, startdatum för uthyrning, "
"slutdatum för uthyrning, uthyrningstyp, uthyrningsbelopp och adress. Ändra "
"uthyrningsstatusen till :guilabel:`Pågående`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "Setting up a running rental record for an employee."
msgstr "Konfigurera en pågående hyrespost för en anställd."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:447
msgid ""
"Rental status definition: :guilabel:`Draft`: Rental just "
"created. :guilabel:`Running`: Rental amount starts adding to payslips from "
"the rental start date. :guilabel:`Expired`: Rental amount is no longer added "
"to payslips. :guilabel:`Cancelled`: Rental has been canceled."
msgstr ""
"Definition av hyresstatus: :guilabel:`Utkast`: Hyra just "
"skapad. :guilabel:`Pågående`: Hyresbelopp börjar läggas till lönebesked från "
"hyresstartdatum. :guilabel:`Utgången`: Hyresbelopp läggs inte längre till "
"lönebesked. :guilabel:`Annullerad`: Hyran har annullerats."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:456
msgid "Run HK payroll"
msgstr "Kör HK-lön"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:458
msgid ""
"Before running payroll, the payroll officer must validate employee work "
"entries to confirm pay accuracy and catch errors. This includes checking "
"that all time off is approved and any overtime is appropriate."
msgstr ""
"Innan löner körs måste löneansvarig validera anställdas arbetsposter för att "
"bekräfta lönenoggrannhet och fånga fel. Detta inkluderar att kontrollera att "
"all ledighet är godkänd och att eventuell övertid är lämplig."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:462
msgid ""
"Work entries sync based on the employee's contract configuration. Odoo pulls "
"from the assigned working schedule, attendance records, planning schedule, "
"and approved time off. Any discrepancies or conflicts must be resolved, then "
"the work entries can be regenerated."
msgstr ""
"Arbetsposter synkroniseras baserat på den anställdes avtalskonfiguration. "
"Odoo hämtar från det tilldelade arbetsschema, närvaroposter, "
"planeringsschema och godkänd ledighet. Eventuella avvikelser eller "
"konflikter måste lösas, sedan kan arbetsposterna regenereras."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:466
msgid ""
"Once everything is correct, draft payslips can be created individually or in "
"groups, referred to in the **Payroll** app as pay runs."
msgstr ""
"När allt är korrekt kan utkast till lönebesked skapas individuellt eller i "
"grupper, vilket i appen **Löner** kallas lönekörningar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:470
msgid ""
"If the work entry or salary inputs for an employee are amended, click the "
"(gear) icon :menuselection:`--> Recompute Whole Sheet` to refresh the "
"payslip's worked days and salary inputs tab."
msgstr ""
"Om arbetsposten eller löneinmatningarna för en anställd ändras, klicka på "
"kugghjulsikonen :menuselection:`--> Beräkna om hela bladet` för att "
"uppdatera lönebeskedets arbetsdagar och löneinmatningsflik."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:475
msgid "Individual payslip"
msgstr "Individuell lönebesked"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:477
msgid "To create an individual payslip in the **Payroll** app:"
msgstr "För att skapa en individuell lönespecifikation i **Löner**-appen:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:479
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Payslips`. "
"Click :guilabel:`New Off-Cycle` to create a payslip for a single employee. "
"Select the employee and period."
msgstr ""
"Gå till :menuselection:`Löner-appen --> Lönebesked --> Lönebesked`. Klicka "
"på :guilabel:`Ny off-cycle` för att skapa ett lönebesked för en enskild "
"anställd. Välj anställd och period."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:483
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically excludes out-of-contract days for pro-rata calculations "
"(i.e., you do not need to select the period according to the employee "
"joining date; Odoo automatically excludes out-of-contract days and reduces "
"the basic salary)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo utesluter automatiskt dagar utanför avtal för pro rata-beräkningar "
"(dvs. du behöver inte välja period enligt den anställdas anställningsdatum; "
"Odoo utesluter automatiskt dagar utanför avtal och reducerar grundlönen)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:487
msgid ""
"Once the payslips are drafted, review them for accuracy. Check "
"the :guilabel:`Worked Days` tab, :guilabel:`Salary Inputs` tab, "
"and :guilabel:`Other info` tab. Ensure the listed worked time is correct, as "
"well as any other inputs. Add any missing optional inputs, such as "
"commissions, tips, reimbursements, etc."
msgstr ""
"När lönebeskeden är utkast, granska dem för noggrannhet. Kontrollera "
"fliken :guilabel:`Arbetade dagar`, fliken :guilabel:`Löneinmatningar` och "
"fliken :guilabel:`Övrig info`. Säkerställ att den listade arbetstiden är "
"korrekt, liksom eventuella andra inmatningar. Lägg till eventuella saknade "
"valfria inmatningar, såsom provisioner, dricks, ersättningar osv."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:492
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Compute Sheet` button, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Validate` button."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Beräkna dokument`, klicka sedan på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Validera`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:495
msgid ""
"Once the payslip is validated, work entries are generated and cannot be "
"edited. Cancel the payslip and set it to draft again if there are any "
"updates."
msgstr ""
"När lönebeskedet är validerat genereras arbetsposter och kan inte redigeras. "
"Avbryt lönebeskedet och ställ tillbaka det till utkast om det finns några "
"uppdateringar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "A completed individual payslip ready for validation."
msgstr "Ett färdigt individuellt lönebesked klart för validering."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:502
msgid "Batch pay run (payslips in groups)"
msgstr "Batchlöneutbetalningar (lönebesked i grupper)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:504
msgid ""
"To create a batch pay run in the **Payroll** app, go "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Pay Runs`. "
"Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new pay run. Select the salary structure, "
"pay schedule, |MPF| scheme, payroll group, and period."
msgstr ""
"För att skapa en batch-löneutbetalning i **Löner**-appen, gå "
"till :menuselection:`Löner-appen --> Lönebesked --> Löneutbetalningar`. "
"Klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa` för att skapa en ny löneutbetalning. Välj "
"lönestruktur, löneintervall, |MPF|-schema, lönegrupp och period."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:509
msgid ""
"The |MPF| scheme and payroll group are optional; if there is only one scheme "
"and one group, you can leave it blank."
msgstr ""
"|MPF|-schemat och lönegruppen är valfria; om det bara finns ett schema och "
"en grupp kan du lämna det tomt."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:512
msgid ""
"Select employee(s). A pay run is created along with the drafted employee "
"payslips. Check all calculations and click the :guilabel:`Validate` button."
msgstr ""
"Välj anställd(a). En löneutbetalning skapas tillsammans med utkast till "
"anställdas lönebesked. Kontrollera alla beräkningar och klicka på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Validera`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "Validating a batch Pay Run."
msgstr "Validering av en batchlöneutbetalning."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:519
msgid ""
"An eMPF report is automatically generated after every pay run. Click the "
"eMPF report or find it in :menuselection:`Reporting --> eMPF Contribution`."
msgstr ""
"En eMPF-rapport genereras automatiskt efter varje löneutbetalning. Klicka på "
"eMPF-rapporten eller hitta den i :menuselection:`Rapportering --> eMPF-"
"bidrag`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:525
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:386
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:438
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:451
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:326
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:380
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:478
msgid "Accounting check"
msgstr "Bokföringskontroll"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:527
msgid ""
"The accounting process when running payroll has two components: creating "
"journal entries, and registering payments. For each component, there are two "
"possible scenarios: individual or batch."
msgstr ""
"Bokföringsprocessen vid lönekörning har två komponenter: skapa "
"verifikationer och registrera betalningar. För varje komponent finns det två "
"möjliga scenarier: individuell eller batch."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:531
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:394
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:446
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:459
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:334
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:388
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:486
msgid "Journal entry creation"
msgstr "Skapa verifikation"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:533
msgid ""
"After payslips are confirmed and validated, journal entries are posted "
"either individually or in a batch. The journal entry is created first as a "
"draft."
msgstr ""
"Efter att lönebesked har bekräftats och validerats bokförs verifikationer "
"antingen individuellt eller i en batch. Verifikationen skapas först som ett "
"utkast."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:537
msgid ""
"It must be decided if journal entries are done individually or in batches "
"(:guilabel:`Batch Account Move Lines`) in the configuration before running "
"payroll."
msgstr ""
"Det måste beslutas om verifikationer görs individuellt eller i batchar "
"(:guilabel:`Batchverifikationsrader`) i konfigurationen innan lönekörning "
"görs."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:541
msgid "Individual journal entries"
msgstr "Individuella verifikationer"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:543
msgid ""
"Without enabling the batch account move line option, you need manual journal "
"entry postings for each payslip, regardless of using a pay run or individual "
"payslip. Select a payslip and click the :guilabel:`Journal Entry (Draft)` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Utan att aktivera alternativet för batch-verifikationsrader måste du "
"manuellt bokföra verifikationer för varje lönebesked, oavsett om du använder "
"en löneutbetalning eller ett individuellt lönebesked. Välj ett lönebesked "
"och klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Verifikation (Utkast)`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:548
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Pay` button appears only for individual journal entries "
"posting. Enabling the :guilabel:`Batch Account Move Lines` option causes "
"this button to disappear."
msgstr ""
"Knappen :guilabel:`Betala` visas endast för individuell "
"verifikationsbokföring. Aktivering av "
"alternativet :guilabel:`Batchverifikationsrader` gör att denna knapp "
"försvinner."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:551
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Post` button. Each payslip is automatically posted as "
"individual journal entries in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Journal "
"entries`."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Bokför`. Varje lönebesked bokförs automatiskt "
"som individuella verifikationer i :menuselection:`Bokföring --> "
"Verifikationer`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "Posting a drafted Journal Entry."
msgstr "Bokföra en verifikation i utkast."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:557
msgid ""
"Four accounts from the Hong Kong CoA are included with the payroll "
"localization:"
msgstr "Fyra konton från Hongkongs kontoplan ingår i lönelokalisering:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:559
msgid ""
"`221001 MPF Accrued (Employer)`: Accrue |MPF| benefits that are spent by "
"employers."
msgstr ""
"`221001 MPF Accrued (Employer)`: Periodisera |MPF|-förmåner som betalas av "
"arbetsgivare."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:560
msgid ""
"`221002 MPF Withheld (Employee)`: Withheld |MPF| benefits that are paid by "
"employees, which will be paid to the |MPF| provider soon."
msgstr ""
"`221002 MPF Withheld (Employee)`: Inneha |MPF|-förmåner som betalas av "
"anställda, vilka kommer att betalas till |MPF|-leverantören inom kort."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:562
msgid ""
"`521700 MPF Contribution (Employer)`: Employer portion of |MPF| "
"contributions expected to be paid to the |MPF| provider soon."
msgstr ""
"`521700 MPF Contribution (Employer)`: Arbetsgivarens del av |MPF|-bidrag som "
"förväntas betalas till |MPF|-leverantören inom kort."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:564
msgid "`221700 Salaries & Wages Payable`: Net salary owed to the employee."
msgstr ""
"`221700 Salaries & Wages Payable`: Nettolön som är skyldig till den "
"anställde."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:567
msgid "Batch entries"
msgstr "Batchinlägg"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:569
msgid ""
"Enabling :guilabel:`Batch Account Move Lines` aggregates all accounting "
"entries for the period into a single account move line. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Journal Entry (Draft)` button (which only appears after "
"enabling the batch account move line in payroll configuration for pay runs). "
"Click the :guilabel:`Post` button. All payslips are automatically "
"consolidated as one journal entry."
msgstr ""
"Genom att aktivera :guilabel:`Batch Account Move Lines` aggregeras alla "
"bokföringsposter för perioden till en enda verifikationsrad. Klicka på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Journal Entry (Draft)` (som endast visas efter att "
"batchverifikationsrader aktiverats i lönekonfiguration för "
"lönutbetalningar). Klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Post`. Alla lönebesked "
"konsolideras automatiskt som en verifikation."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:575
msgid "Register payment"
msgstr "Registrera betalning"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:577
msgid ""
"After the journal entries are validated, Odoo generates payment report files."
msgstr ""
"Efter att verifikationerna har validerats genererar Odoo "
"betalningsrapportfiler."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:580
msgid ""
"To generate payments from payslips, an employee must have a trusted bank "
"account. If the employee's bank account is not marked as trusted, payment "
"files cannot be generated."
msgstr ""
"För att generera betalningar från lönebesked måste en anställd ha ett "
"betrott bankkonto. Om den anställdes bankkonto inte är markerat som betrott "
"kan betalningsfiler inte genereras."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:583
msgid ""
"**HSBC Auto Pay Report**: Click :guilabel:`HSBC Auto Pay Report`. (You must "
"configure the HSBC Autopay bank account in configuration for this button to "
"appear). Configure the HSBC Autopay report information. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Confirm` button. Click the download icon to download the "
"`.apc` HSBC report."
msgstr ""
"**HSBC Auto Pay Report**: Klicka på :guilabel:`HSBC Auto Pay Report`. (Du "
"måste konfigurera HSBC Autopay-bankkontot i konfigurationen för att denna "
"knapp ska visas). Konfigurera HSBC Autopay-rapportinformationen. Klicka på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Confirm`. Klicka på nedladdningsikonen för att ladda ner "
"`.apc` HSBC-rapporten."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:587
msgid ""
"**Payment Report**: Click :guilabel:`Payment Report`. Payments can be "
"grouped by partner if there is a partner associated with a salary rule. "
"Select the export format and click :guilabel:`Generate` to download the CSV."
msgstr ""
"**Payment Report**: Klicka på :guilabel:`Payment Report`. Betalningar kan "
"grupperas efter partner om det finns en partner kopplad till en löneregel. "
"Välj exportformat och klicka på :guilabel:`Generate` för att ladda ner CSV-"
"filen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:594
msgid "Payroll reporting"
msgstr "Lönerapportering"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:596
msgid ""
"The Hong Kong localization contains several reports unique to HK, which "
"provide eMPF contribution reports and auto-generated IR56 reports (both in "
"`.xml` and PDF formats)."
msgstr ""
"Hongkonglokaliseringen innehåller flera rapporter som är unika för HK, vilka "
"tillhandahåller eMPF-avgiftsrapporter och automatiskt genererade IR56-"
"rapporter (både i `.xml`- och PDF-format)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:600
msgid ""
"Payslips must be validated in order to generate eMPF reports and IR56 "
"reports."
msgstr ""
"Lönebesked måste valideras för att generera eMPF-rapporter och IR56-"
"rapporter."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:603
msgid "eMPF contribution reports"
msgstr "eMPF-avgiftsrapporter"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:605
msgid "eMPF contribution reports can be generated in two ways:"
msgstr "eMPF-avgiftsrapporter kan genereras på två sätt:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:607
msgid ""
"**Auto-generated reports**: After every pay run, eMPF contributions reports "
"can be found in :menuselection:`Payroll app --> eMPF Contributions`."
msgstr ""
"**Automatiskt genererade rapporter**: Efter varje löneutbetalning kan eMPF-"
"bidragsrapporter hittas i :menuselection:`Löner-appen --> eMPF-bidrag`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:609
msgid ""
"**Manually generated reports**: eMPF contribution reports can be generated "
"manually only after the payslips are validated."
msgstr ""
"**Manuellt genererade rapporter**: eMPF-bidragsrapporter kan genereras "
"manuellt endast efter att lönebesked har validerats."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:612
msgid ""
"Click :menuselection:`Payroll --> eMPF Contributions`. "
"Click :guilabel:`New`. Select the contribution period, scheme, and payroll "
"group to generate the report."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på :menuselection:`Löner --> eMPF-bidrag`. Klicka på :guilabel:`Ny`. "
"Välj bidragsperiod, schema och lönegrupp för att skapa rapporten."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:615
msgid "**Member status**:"
msgstr "**Medlemsstatus**:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:617
msgid ":guilabel:`Existing Member`: Employees making monthly contributions."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Befintlig medlem`: Anställda som betalar månatliga bidrag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:618
msgid ""
":guilabel:`New Member`: New employees in holiday periods for contributions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ny medlem`: Nya anställda under semesterperioder för bidrag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:619
msgid ":guilabel:`Terminated Member`: Employee leaving the company."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Avslutad medlem`: Anställd som lämnar företaget."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:621
msgid "**Termination payment**:"
msgstr "**Avgångsbetalning**:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:623
msgid ""
":guilabel:`L`: Appears if a leaving employee has a long service payment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`L`: Visas om en avgående anställd har en betalning för lång "
"tjänstgöring."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:624
msgid ":guilabel:`S`: Appears if a leaving employee has a severance payment."
msgstr ":guilabel:`S`: Visas om en avgående anställd har ett avgångsvederlag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "The eMPF Contribution report screen."
msgstr "Skärmen för eMPF-bidragsrapport."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:630
msgid ""
"Each contribution line can be amended (i.e., member status and termination "
"payment type can be updated or deleted). However, relevant income and "
"contributions cannot be edited. If the contribution line for an employee is "
"amended, click the (gear) icon :menuselection:`--> Recompute contribution` "
"to refresh the information."
msgstr ""
"Varje bidragsrad kan ändras (dvs. medlemsstatus och typ av "
"avslutningsbetalning kan uppdateras eller raderas). Relevanta inkomster och "
"bidrag kan dock inte redigeras. Om bidragsraden för en anställd ändras, "
"klicka på kugghjulsikonen :menuselection:`--> Beräkna om bidrag` för att "
"uppdatera informationen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:635
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Validate` button. If there are no errors, eMPF "
"contribution reports are generated in three different `.csv` files inside a "
"zip file, which are ready to upload to the eMPF portal: `new employees.csv`, "
"`contributions.csv`, and `terminated employees.csv`."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Validera`. Om det inte finns några fel "
"genereras eMPF-bidragsrapporter i tre olika `.csv`-filer i en zip-fil, som "
"är klara att laddas upp till eMPF-portalen: `new employees.csv`, "
"`contributions.csv` och `terminated employees.csv`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:640
msgid ""
"Warnings are mainly raised to align with eMPF requirements for employee "
"information. Employees **must** be 18-60 years of age, and the phone number "
"must be a valid Hong Kong phone number."
msgstr ""
"Varningar väcks huvudsakligen för att stämma överens med eMPF-krav för "
"anställdas information. Anställda **måste** vara 18-60 år gamla, och "
"telefonnumret måste vara ett giltigt Hongkong-telefonnummer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:644
msgid "IR56 reports"
msgstr "IR56-rapporter"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:646
msgid "Odoo provides four |IRD| reports:"
msgstr "Odoo tillhandahåller fyra |IRD|-rapporter:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:648
msgid ""
":guilabel:`IR56B (Annual Return)`: The Employer's Return of Remuneration and "
"Pensions; submitted annually for all existing employees."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`IR56B (årsrapport)`: Arbetsgivarens redovisning av ersättningar "
"och pensioner; lämnas in årligen för alla befintliga anställda."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:650
msgid ""
":guilabel:`IR56E (New Hire)`: Notification of Commencement of Employment; "
"submitted for new employees within three months of their start date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`IR56E (nyanställning)`: Anmälan om påbörjad anställning; lämnas "
"in för nya anställda inom tre månader från deras startdatum."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:652
msgid ""
":guilabel:`IR56F (Termination)`: Notification of Cessation of Employment for "
"employees leaving the company but remaining in Hong Kong."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`IR56F (uppsägning)`: Anmälan om upphörande av anställning för "
"anställda som lämnar företaget men stannar kvar i Hongkong."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:654
msgid ""
":guilabel:`IR56G (Departure)`: Notification of Cessation of Employment for "
"employees leaving Hong Kong permanently or for a long period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`IR56G (avresa)`: Anmälan om upphörande av anställning för "
"anställda som lämnar Hongkong permanent eller för en lång period."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:658
msgid ""
"When generating the IR56B in Odoo, the system automatically looks at the "
"date on the payslips to pull all records falling within the last year, April "
"1 to March 31 of the current year. Once an employer files an IR56F or IR56G "
"for an employee, it should not be included again in the annual IR56B to "
"avoid double-reporting income."
msgstr ""
"När IR56B skapas i Odoo tittar systemet automatiskt på datumet på "
"lönespecifikationerna för att hämta alla handlingar som faller inom det "
"senaste året, 1 april till 31 mars innevarande år. När en arbetsgivare "
"lämnat in en IR56F eller IR56G för en anställd bör den inte inkluderas igen "
"i den årliga IR56B för att undvika dubbelrapportering av inkomst."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:664
msgid "Generating an IR56 report"
msgstr "Skapa en IR56-rapport"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:666
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Reporting`, and select one of the "
"IR56B/E/F/G sheet options. Click :guilabel:`New`. Fill in the relevant "
"information for the |IRD| report (e.g., :guilabel:`Submission "
"Date`, :guilabel:`Year of Employer's Return`). Click "
"the :guilabel:`Populate` button."
msgstr ""
"Gå till :menuselection:`Löner-appen --> Rapporter` och välj ett av "
"alternativen IR56B/E/F/G-blad. Klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa`. Fyll i relevant "
"information för |IRD|-rapporten "
"(t.ex. :guilabel:`Inlämningsdatum`, :guilabel:`År för arbetsgivarens "
"deklaration`). Klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Fyll i`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:671
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Create XML` and :guilabel:`Eligible Employees` smart buttons "
"appear if there is relevant generated payslip information. "
"Click :guilabel:`Create XML` to download the XML report. "
"Click :guilabel:`Eligible Employees` to view the list and "
"select :guilabel:`Generate PDFs` to queue PDF document generation."
msgstr ""
"De smarta knapparna :guilabel:`Skapa XML` och :guilabel:`Berättigade "
"anställda` visas om det finns relevant genererad "
"lönespecifikationsinformation. Klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa XML` för att ladda "
"ned XML-rapporten. Klicka på :guilabel:`Berättigade anställda` för att visa "
"listan och välj :guilabel:`Generera PDF-filer` för att köa PDF-"
"dokumentgenerering."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "The completed IR56B report screen with downloadable files."
msgstr "Den slutförda IR56B-rapportskärmen med nedladdningsbara filer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:682
msgid "Payslip tabs"
msgstr "Flikar för lönespecifikation"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:684
msgid ""
"Different tabs in each payslip define worked days used to calculate payroll, "
"additional salary inputs to add to the payslip, how salary computation is "
"handled, and other info that impacts the payslip."
msgstr ""
"Olika flikar i varje lönespecifikation definierar arbetade dagar som används "
"för att beräkna lön, ytterligare löneuppgifter att lägga till i "
"lönespecifikationen, hur löneberäkning hanteras och annan information som "
"påverkar lönespecifikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:688
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Worked Days`: Details all the individual attendance records for "
"the time period, including both worked time and any time off taken. It is "
"auto-populated and cannot be edited."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbetade dagar`: Detaljerar alla individuella närvarohandlingar "
"för tidsperioden, inklusive både arbetad tid och eventuell ledig tid. Den "
"fylls i automatiskt och kan inte redigeras."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:690
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salary Inputs`: Details where additional salary inputs are "
"listed, such as deductions, reimbursements, and expenses. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add Inputs` to manually include them."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Löneuppgifter`: Detaljerar där ytterligare löneuppgifter listas, "
"såsom avdrag, ersättningar och utlägg. Klicka på :guilabel:`Lägg till "
"uppgifter` för att manuellt inkludera dem."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:692
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salary Computation`: Where all the individual salary rules are "
"listed and calculated, including everything from the employee's salary to "
"all the deductions, taxes, and |MPF| contributions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Löneberäkning`: Där alla individuella löneregler listas och "
"beräknas, inklusive allt från den anställdas lön till alla avdrag, skatter "
"och |MPF|-bidrag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:695
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Other Info`: Shows the :guilabel:`Average Daily Wage` rate that "
"is used to calculate statutory HK holidays and entitlements. Also contains "
"the :guilabel:`End-of-Year Pay`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Övrig information`: Visar dagslönesatsen :guilabel:`Average Daily "
"Wage` som används för att beräkna lagstadgade HK-helgdagar och rättigheter. "
"Innehåller också :guilabel:`Årsslutsbetalning`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:699
msgid ""
"Manually adding an end-of-year payment to a specific payslip may require "
"saving the record manually, clicking the :icon:`fa-"
"gear` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon, and then selecting :guilabel:`Recompute "
"Whole Sheet`."
msgstr ""
"Att manuellt lägga till en årsslutsbetalning till ett specifikt lönebesked "
"kan kräva att du sparar posten manuellt, klickar på ikonen :icon:`fa-"
"gear` :guilabel:`(Åtgärder)` och sedan väljer :guilabel:`Beräkna om hela "
"bladet`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:None
msgid "Other info tab under payslip"
msgstr "Fliken övrig information under lönespecifikation"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:709
msgid "Understanding Hong Kong payroll"
msgstr "Förstå Hongkong-löner"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:711
msgid ""
"In Hong Kong, payroll calculations typically follow a standard daily wage "
"formula:"
msgstr ""
"I Hongkong följer löneberäkningar vanligtvis en standardformel för daglön:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:713
msgid ""
"\\text{Daily Wage} = \\frac{\\text{Total wage in a month}}{\\text{Total days "
"in a month}}"
msgstr ""
"\\text{Daglön} = \\frac{\\text{Total lön under en månad}}{\\text{Totalt "
"antal dagar i en månad}}"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:717
msgid ""
"However, the Employment (Amendment) Ordinance 2007 (often referred to as the "
"\"713 Ordinance\") requires employers to use the Average Daily Wage (ADW) "
"when calculating specific statutory entitlements. Statutory entitlements "
"requiring ADW include: holiday pay, annual leave pay, sickness allowance, "
"maternity leave pay, paternity leave pay, end of year payment, and payment "
"in lieu of notice."
msgstr ""
"Employment (Amendment) Ordinance 2007 (ofta kallad \"713-förordningen\") "
"kräver dock att arbetsgivare använder den genomsnittliga daglönen (ADW) när "
"de beräknar specifika lagstadgade rättigheter. Lagstadgade rättigheter som "
"kräver ADW inkluderar: helgdagslön, årlig semesterlön, sjukbidrag, "
"föräldraledighetsersättning, faderskapsledighetsersättning, "
"årsskiftesbetalning och betalning i stället för uppsägning."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:723
msgid ""
"To calculate the ADW, use the earnings and days from the preceding 12 months:"
msgstr ""
"För att beräkna ADW, använd inkömster och dagar från de föregående 12 "
"månaderna:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:725
msgid ""
"\\text{ADW} = \\frac{\\text{Total Wage in 12-month period} - \\text{Wages of "
"Non-full pay}}{\\text{Total Days in 12-month period} - \\text{Days of Non-"
"full pay}}"
msgstr ""
"\\text{ADW} = \\frac{\\text{Total lön under 12-månadersperiod} - "
"\\text{Löner för ej hel betalning}}{\\text{Totalt antal dagar under 12-"
"månadersperiod} - \\text{Dagar med ej hel betalning}}"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:729
msgid "Where:"
msgstr "Där:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:731
msgid ""
"**Total Wage in 12-month period**: All earnings in the last 12 months (e.g., "
"basic salary, overtime, commissions, and allowances)."
msgstr ""
"**Total lön under 12-månadersperiod**: Alla inkömster under de senaste 12 "
"månaderna (t.ex. grundlön, övertid, provisioner och tillägg)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:733
msgid ""
"**Wages of Non-full pay**: Any wages paid at less than the full rate (e.g., "
"sick leave, maternity/paternity leave, etc)."
msgstr ""
"**Löner för ej hel betalning**: Alla löner som betalas till mindre än full "
"takt (t.ex. sjukledighet, föräldra-/faderskapsledighet osv)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:735
msgid ""
"**Total Days in 12-month period**: Total calendar days in the 12-month "
"reference period."
msgstr ""
"**Totala dagar i 12-månadersperiod**: Totala kalenderdagar i 12-"
"månadersreferensperioden."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:736
msgid ""
"**Days of Non-full pay**: The specific number of days for which the employee "
"was not paid in full."
msgstr ""
"**Dagar utan full lön**: Det specifika antalet dagar för vilka den anställde "
"inte fick full lön."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:739
msgid ""
"Odoo requires historical payroll records to calculate ADW accurately. If no "
"prior records exist, the ADW calculation always results in zero."
msgstr ""
"Odoo kräver historiska lönehandlingar för att beräkna ADW korrekt. Om inga "
"tidigare handlingar finns resulterar ADW-beräkningen alltid i noll."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:745
msgid "Calculation examples"
msgstr "Beräkningsexempel"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:748
msgid "CAP 57: Employees Monthly Pay"
msgstr "CAP 57: Anställdas månadslöner"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:750
msgid ""
"Calculate the March payslip for Natalie Chan who joined Jan 1, 2026, with a "
"monthly salary of 20K."
msgstr ""
"Beräkna mars lönebesked för Natalie Chan som anställdes 1 januari 2026 med "
"en månadslön på 20K."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:752
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:786
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:817
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:857
msgid "Jan: Monthly salary 20K."
msgstr "Jan: Månadslön 20K."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:753
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:787
msgid "Feb: Monthly salary 20K and 5K commission."
msgstr "Feb: Månadslön 20K och 5K provision."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:754
msgid ""
"Mar: Apply for one full-paid paternity leave and one sick leave with 80% ADW "
"in March."
msgstr ""
"Mar: Tillämpa för en helbetald faderskapsledighet och en sjukledighet med "
"80% ADW i mars."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:756
msgid "**Calculate ADW:**"
msgstr "**Beräkna ADW:**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:758
msgid "Total wages earned: 20,000 + 25,000 = 45,000"
msgstr "Totala intjänade löner: 20 000 + 25 000 = 45 000"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:759
msgid "Total days: 31 + 28 = 59 days"
msgstr "Totala dagar: 31 + 28 = 59 dagar"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:761
msgid "\\text{ADW} = \\frac{45,000}{59} = 762.71"
msgstr "\\text{ADW} = \\frac{45,000}{59} = 762.71"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:765
msgid "**Calculate leave payment and total wages:**"
msgstr "**Beräkna ledighetsbetalning och totala löner:**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:767
msgid "One full day paternity leave (full paid ADW) = 762.71"
msgstr "En hel dag faderskapsledighet (helbetald ADW) = 762.71"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:768
msgid "One full day sick leave 80% (80% paid ADW) = 762.71 * 80% = 610.17"
msgstr "En hel dags sjukledighet 80% (80% betald ADW) = 762,71 * 80% = 610,17"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:769
msgid ""
"Attendance = Daily wage * num of working days = (20,000 / 31) * 20 = "
"12,903.23"
msgstr "Närvaro = Dagslön * antal arbetsdagar = (20 000 / 31) * 20 = 12 903.23"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:770
msgid "Weekend = Daily wage * num of weekends = (20,000 / 31) * 9 = 5,806.45"
msgstr "Helg = Dagslön * antal helger = (20 000 / 31) * 9 = 5 806.45"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:771
msgid ""
"Wages earned for Mar = 762.71 + 610.17 + 12,903.23 + 5,806.45 = 20,082.56"
msgstr ""
"Intjänade löner för mars = 762.71 + 610.17 + 12 903.23 + 5 806.45 = 20 082.56"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:773
msgid "**Calculate HK compliant payslip:**"
msgstr "**Beräkna HK-kompatibelt lönebesked:**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:775
msgid "Basic salary = 20,082.56"
msgstr "Grundlön = 20 082,56"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:776
msgid "|MPF| gross = 20,082.56"
msgstr "|MPF| brutto = 20 082,56"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:777
msgid "Employee mandatory contribution = 20,082.56 * 5% = 1,004.13"
msgstr "Obligatoriskt arbetstagaravgift = 20 082,56 * 5% = 1 004,13"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:778
msgid "Net salary earned for Mar = 20,082.56 - 1,004.13 = 19,078.43"
msgstr "Nettolön för mars = 20 082,56 - 1 004,13 = 19 078,43"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:781
msgid "CAP 57: Payment in Lieu of Notice"
msgstr "CAP 57: Betalning i stället för uppsägning"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:783
msgid ""
"Calculate payment in lieu of notice for Natalie Chan who joined Jan 1, 2026, "
"with a monthly salary of 20K and was fired in Mar with one month of payment "
"in lieu of notice."
msgstr ""
"Beräkna betalning i stället för uppsägning för Natalie Chan som började 1 "
"januari 2026, med en månadslön på 20K och blev uppsagd i mars med en månads "
"betalning i stället för uppsägning."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:789
msgid "**1. Calculate average monthly salary:**"
msgstr "**1. Beräkna genomsnittlig månadslön:**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:791
msgid "Days in average month: 365 days / 12 months = 30.41667 days"
msgstr "Dagar i genomsnittsmånad: 365 dagar / 12 månader = 30,41667 dagar"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:793
msgid ""
"\\text{Average monthly salary} = \\text{ADW} \\times \\text{Days in average "
"month}"
msgstr ""
"\\text{Genomsnittlig månadslön} = \\text{ADW} \\times \\text{Dagar i "
"genomsnittsmånad}"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:797
msgid "\\text{Average monthly salary} = 762.71 \\times 30.41667 = 23,199.15"
msgstr "\\text{Genomsnittlig månadslön} = 762,71 \\times 30,41667 = 23 199,15"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:801
msgid "**2. Calculate payment in lieu of notice:**"
msgstr "**2. Beräkna betalning i stället för uppsägning:**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:803
msgid ""
"\\text{Payment in Lieu of Notice} = \\text{Average monthly salary} \\times "
"\\text{Notice Period}"
msgstr ""
"\\text{Betalning i stället för uppsägning} = \\text{Genomsnittlig månadslön} "
"\\times \\text{Uppsägningstid}"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:807
msgid "\\text{Payment in Lieu of Notice} = 23,199.15 \\times 1 = 23,199.15"
msgstr ""
"\\text{Betalning i stället för uppsägning} = 23 199,15 \\times 1 = 23 199,15"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:812
msgid "CAP 57: Long Service Payment"
msgstr "CAP 57: Avgångsersättning"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:814
msgid ""
"Calculate long service payment for Anthony Choi who joined Jan 1, 2021, with "
"a monthly salary of 20K and left the company on Feb 28, 2026."
msgstr ""
"Beräkna avgångsväderlag för Anthony Choi som började 1 januari 2021, med en "
"månadslön på 20 000 och lämnade företaget 28 februari 2026."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:818
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:858
msgid "Feb: Monthly salary 20K."
msgstr "Februari: Månadslön 20K."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:820
msgid "**1. Calculate long service payment:**"
msgstr "**1. Beräkna avgångsersättning:**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:822
msgid ""
"Last month's monthly salary record must be in Odoo to calculate SP/LSP. The "
"LSP is based on pre/post transition according to the `HK Labour calculator "
"<https://www.lr.labour.gov.hk/web/en/calculator/index.html>`_:"
msgstr ""
"Senaste månadens månadslönepost måste finnas i Odoo för att beräkna SP/LSP. "
"LSP baseras på för/efter övergång enligt `HK Labour calculator <https://"
"www.lr.labour.gov.hk/web/en/calculator/index.html>`_:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:826
msgid ""
"\\text{LSP} = \\left(\\text{Last Full Month's Wages} \\times \\frac{2}"
"{3}\\right) \\times \\text{Years of Service}"
msgstr ""
"\\text{LSP} = \\left(\\text{Senaste hela månadens löner} \\times \\frac{2}"
"{3}\\right) \\times \\text{Anställningsår}"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:830
msgid ""
"\\text{LSP} = \\text{Pre-transition portion} + \\text{Post-transition "
"portion}"
msgstr "\\text{LSP} = \\text{Del före övergång} + \\text{Del efter övergång}"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:834
msgid ""
"\\text{LSP} = \\left(20,000 \\times \\frac{2}{3} \\times \\left(4 + "
"\\frac{120}{365}\\right)\\right) + \\left(20,000 \\times \\frac{2}{3} "
"\\times \\left(0 + \\frac{304}{365}\\right)\\right)"
msgstr ""
"\\text{LSP} = \\left(20,000 \\times \\frac{2}{3} \\times \\left(4 + "
"\\frac{120}{365}\\right)\\right) + \\left(20,000 \\times \\frac{2}{3} "
"\\times \\left(0 + \\frac{304}{365}\\right)\\right)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:838
msgid "\\text{LSP} = 57,716.89 + 11,105.02 = 68,821.91"
msgstr "\\text{LSP} = 57,716.89 + 11,105.02 = 68,821.91"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:842
msgid "**2. Calculate long service payment with MPF offset:**"
msgstr "**2. Beräkna långtjänstbetalning med MPF-avräkning:**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:844
msgid ""
"**Pre-transition offset**: Total employee mandatory contributions made "
"before May 2025 can be excluded from the long service payment. Example: If "
"Anthony's total employee mandatory contribution before May 2025 was "
"7,047.98, this amount is treated as a pre-transition offset and excluded "
"from the long service payment."
msgstr ""
"**Förövergångsavräkning**: Totala obligatoriska anställdas avgifter som "
"gjorts före maj 2025 kan exkluderas från långtjänstbetalningen. Exempel: Om "
"Anthonys totala obligatoriska anställdas avgift före maj 2025 var 7,047.98, "
"behandlas detta belopp som en förövergångsavräkning och exkluderas från "
"långtjänstbetalningen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:848
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:888
msgid ""
"**Post-transition offset**: Employee mandatory contributions made after May "
"2025 cannot be excluded (no post-transition offset)."
msgstr ""
"**Efterövergångsavräkning**: Obligatoriska anställdas avgifter som gjorts "
"efter maj 2025 kan inte exkluderas (ingen efterövergångsavräkning)."

